org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process

Class ProcessDeploymentInfoSearchDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process.ProcessDeploymentInfoSearchDescriptor

  • public class ProcessDeploymentInfoSearchDescriptor
extends Object
    Search descriptors are used to filter / sort results of a generic search.
    ProcessDeploymentInfoSearchDescriptor defines the fields that can be used as filters or sort fields on List<ProcessDeploymentInfo> returning methods.
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Zhao Na, Celine Souchet, Matthieu Chaffotte
    See Also:
    ProcessAPI, ProcessDeploymentInfo, ProcessDefinition
